1
00:00:26,450 --> 00:00:26,900
[Name: Du Cong]

2
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:40,320
Look at these big fruits.

3
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:41,050
How nice.

4
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,430
I told you so, didn't I?

5
00:00:42,430 --> 00:00:43,240
They're all nice fruits.

6
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:43,710
Yes.

7
00:00:44,390 --> 00:00:45,880
You'll be in charge of grocery shopping
from now on.

8
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:47,070
I'd rather stay out of it.

9
00:00:47,070 --> 00:00:47,800
Absolutely.

10
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:48,710
Dad,

11
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,430
Mom,

12
00:00:52,070 --> 00:00:53,470
I'm such an unfilial son.

13
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,600
This parting could be...

14
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:04,879
♪ The stars twinkle, the moon curves ♪

15
00:01:08,870 --> 00:01:13,570
♪ A gentle breeze
sways the willow branches ♪

16
00:01:14,150 --> 00:01:15,550
It's the two of you again.

17
00:01:16,030 --> 00:01:19,289
♪ The two of us, working late at night,
sneak up to the base of the wall ♪

18
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:20,480
The same bad thing
could happen once or twice,

19
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,680
but not three or four times!

20
00:01:22,789 --> 00:01:23,520
[Do not trample on the plants]

21
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:26,030
♪ Sneaking around, peeking through ♪

22
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:36,590
"Never cave in to reality."

23
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:02,680
Never cave in to reality.

24
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,400
Never cave in to reality.

25
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,590
Never cave in to reality.

26
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:19,390
Never cave in to reality.

27
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:48,440
[Born with Luck]

28
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:51,380
[Episode 19]

29
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:57,490
[Forensic Lab of Sanjiangkou
Municipal Public Security Bureau]

30
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,870
The substance found at the scene
last night

31
00:03:57,510 --> 00:03:58,620
[Physical Evidence Examination Report]

32
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:00,980
is human blood.

33
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:10,680
Judging from

34
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,870
what we know of now,

35
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:12,830
the dead

36
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,660
is most likely Liu Bei.

37
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:16,870
So, now, our primary goal

38
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,480
is to find

39
00:04:18,829 --> 00:04:21,089
Liu Bei and the killer.

40
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,560
Alive or dead, there has to be proof.

41
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:24,750
That is to say,

42
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,390
all the vehicles and people

43
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:27,870
passing by the intersection

44
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,270
near Xiangji Temple must be

45
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:30,000
looked into.

46
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,360
It is the evening rush hour.

47
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,000
The traffic conditions
at the intersection are complex,

48
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,390
with a large flow of people.

49
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:36,120
Chief Zhang,

50
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,690
we need more manpower.

51
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,040
Li Qian,

52
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:41,680
give them a hand.

53
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:49,240
It's temporary.

54
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,020
You'll only spent

55
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:51,360
a couple of days with them.

56
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,600
Just obey the order.

57
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,330
You are a girl.

58
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:56,190
Chief Zhang had no other choice.

59
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:03,530
He just caved under pressure.

60
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,190
Where was I?

61
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,390
We need to find Liu Bei and the killer.

62
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:12,390
Liu Bei and the killer. Right.

63
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,670
We propose to merge

64
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:14,620
this case

65
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,630
with Zhou Rong's case.

66
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,800
What do you think?

67
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,500
Human blood was found,

68
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,190
but how do we prove

69
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:22,050
it's Liu Bei's?

70
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,430
Even if it is Liu Bei's,

71
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:25,030
how do we prove he was killed?

72
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,940
The surveillance footage

73
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,920
shows that Liu Bei

74
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,720
came in carrying a suitcase.

75
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:38,790
So these are his footprints.

76
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,409
But the man who left was not Liu Bei.

77
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,159
This is a mark left by the suitcase wheels

78
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,690
when this man went away.

79
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,950
Pay attention to this trail.

80
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:48,720
It's deeper.

81
00:05:50,270 --> 00:05:52,000
There is only one possibility.

82
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,630
That is, the dead

83
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:53,760
was in the suitcase.

84
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,730
And this dead man

85
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,580
was Liu Bei.

86
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,190
But there are barely

87
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:59,190
any signs of a struggle at the scene.

88
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:01,120
The killer took his target down
with only one move.

89
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,380
With Liu Bei's skills,

90
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,560
who could be so capable

91
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,960
as to kill him instantly?

92
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:10,000
There must be someone as strong as that.

93
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,560
Who?

94
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:14,720
Yeah.

95
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:16,600
Who?

96
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,620
Finding out who it is

97
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,430
is what we are going

98
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,360
to do next.

99
00:06:22,430 --> 00:06:22,870
Right?

100
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:25,010
Chief, please go on.

101
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,390
We watched the surveillance footage

102
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,320
near the crime scene this morning,

103
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,400
and found a suspicious vehicle.

104
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,659
This car also has a fake plate.

105
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,000
In the past few days, this car

106
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,240
got in two traffic accidents

107
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,190
with cars owned by Rongcheng Group.

108
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:38,650
Li Qian,

109
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:39,480
when your car

110
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,140
rear-ended

111
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,630
that Rongcheng Group's car that day,

112
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:43,600
the car that fled the scene was this one.

113
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,860
Were all the incidents

114
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,050
just coincidental?

115
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:48,120
I don't think so.

116
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,560
These two people were highly likely

117
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,890
in cahoots with Liu Bei,

118
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:53,270
so they also sneaked into

119
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:54,330
Zhou Rong's manor.

120
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:56,560
This provides an answer

121
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,920
to Li Qian's question just now.

122
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,450
It is true

123
00:06:58,670 --> 00:07:00,240
that Liu Bei was a great fighter.

124
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,040
But what if he was

125
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,700
caught completely off guard?

126
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,500
What if he was killed by an acquaintance?

127
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,410
This is my guess:

128
00:07:09,820 --> 00:07:11,080
it was these two people

129
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:13,200
who robbed Zhou Rong

130
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,260
and beat up Lang Bowen.

131
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:17,630
Suppose they were indeed

132
00:07:17,650 --> 00:07:18,850
working with Liu Bei,

133
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,970
then that phone and the suitcase

134
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,700
must be in their hands now.

135
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,330
I suggest we treat these two people

136
00:07:25,330 --> 00:07:27,100
as our primary targets now.

137
00:07:27,130 --> 00:07:27,900
I agree.

138
00:07:28,510 --> 00:07:29,040
I agree.

139
00:07:29,060 --> 00:07:29,720
-Agreed.
-Agreed.

140
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,240
I agree.

141
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:31,370
-Agreed.
-I agree.

142
00:07:32,590 --> 00:07:34,120
If you all concur with me...

143
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,020
I beg to differ.

144
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,920
Why?

145
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:40,450
It doesn't seem to me that Zhou Rong

146
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:42,210
was robbed by these two people.

147
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,760
I've seen those two guys.

148
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:45,800
Hadn't you been knocked out by then?

149
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,720
I woke up later and got

150
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,120
a blurry glimpse of them.

151
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:49,630
They don't look like the robbers.

152
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:51,890
Didn't you say their faces were covered?

153
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:55,610
That's why I said
they didn't look like the robbers.

154
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:03,720
Li Qian just made

155
00:08:04,690 --> 00:08:06,150
a rather good point.

156
00:08:06,950 --> 00:08:08,270
Everyone, try to collect

157
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:09,670
evidence in this regard.

158
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,640
Got it.

159
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,980
Before new evidence is found,

160
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,630
these two people

161
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:15,360
are still our primary targets.

162
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,190
Agreed?

163
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,070
Agreed.

164
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,390
Find out who they are.

165
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,310
I just did.

166
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,700
The driver is Mao Hongwei,

167
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:33,650
nicknamed Mao.

168
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:34,240
The other man

169
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,840
should be a fellow of his, Xia Tinggang.

170
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,150
They operate a scrap yard

171
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:41,299
[Building 2]

172
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,200
near the chemical industrial zone.

173
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:00,570
Have you...

174
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,050
seen a dead body?

175
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:06,120
N-Not when it's so close.

176
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,600
Y-You go take a look.

177
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,720
No, you do it.

178
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,680
L-Let's do it together then.

179
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,660
What are you doing?

180
00:09:42,270 --> 00:09:43,330
What are you doing?

181
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,170
What is this?

182
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:00,320
This is...

183
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,450
the murder weapon.

184
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,730
No, it's not.

185
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,080
Didn't you see that guy's

186
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:07,720
slit on the neck?

187
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,250
It must be caused by a knife.

188
00:10:10,150 --> 00:10:11,410
Let me venture a guess.

189
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,000
The killer first knocked out
the dead with this,

190
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,320
and then slit his neck
with a knife.

191
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,070
Otherwise, why would

192
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:16,600
this thing

193
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,980
be placed beside the body?

194
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:18,840
I bet the killer meant to

195
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,480
dump the body

196
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,280
and throw away the weapon later.

197
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:23,550
Right?

198
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,480
Quite smug, aren't you?

199
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,540
Dump the body, huh?

200
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,060
Dump the body, huh?

201
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,120
I sent you out to snatch money.

202
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:31,960
Why did you bring back

203
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,550
a dead body instead?

204
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:32,960
W-Who

205
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,750
would've known this could happen?

206
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:35,750
That man looks...

207
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,200
just like Sakuragi Hanamichi.

208
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,930
Who would know he is a murderer?

209
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,080
How was I supposed to know

210
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,630
there was a body in this suitcase?

211
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:42,550
Would I have known that?

212
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,390
You didn't expect it, did you?

213
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,750
I didn't expect any of this.

214
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:45,150
Didn't expect this?

215
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:45,790
Why were you so careless?

216
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:46,720
How could you be this ignorant?

217
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,390
What's this for?

218
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,640
Now see what you've started.

219
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:52,000
Instead of money, you brought

220
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,400
such grave trouble back.

221
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,720
Let's call the police then.

222
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,470
K-K-Keep your voice down.

223
00:10:57,820 --> 00:11:00,900
[Taxi]

224
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:02,990
Call the police, huh?

225
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:04,890
It's true

226
00:11:05,270 --> 00:11:06,870
that we didn't kill this man.

227
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,410
But for driving this fake taxi

228
00:11:09,410 --> 00:11:10,290
for robbery,

229
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,080
we'll still be put in prison, won't we?

230
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,960
Which will keep you

231
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,200
behind bars longer,

232
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:15,120
driving a fake taxi

233
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,700
for robbery, or killing a man?

234
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:22,320
[Taxi]

235
00:11:17,390 --> 00:11:19,250
No, we didn't kill this man.

236
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:21,320
And I didn't borrow that money.

237
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:23,250
Why should I be put in jail with you?

238
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,390
Driving a fake taxi

239
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:26,320
for robbery

240
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,030
was your idea.

241
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,790
-I told you to keep it down!
-I can prove that!

242
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:30,250
I should have a say in this!

243
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:33,130
C-Come over here and talk.

244
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,870
I won't hit you.

245
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,370
Come and talk to me in a lower voice.

246
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,480
What if you hit me?

247
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:40,120
I...

248
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:41,760
If I hit you,

249
00:11:41,790 --> 00:11:42,960
I'll die without descendants.

250
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,490
Alright?

251
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,440
Tinggang,

252
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,050
let's throw the suitcase away.

253
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,320
Where?

254
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,890
Anywhere is fine.

255
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,450
The farther the better.

256
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:26,510
Never cave in to reality.

257
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,120
They've been disturbing

258
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:45,200
all the neighbors.

259
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,440
They should've been caught long ago.

260
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,600
They should've been dealt with long ago.

261
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:49,600
See, you guys waited so long to do so.

262
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,630
Where have they gone?

263
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:58,260
Chief,

264
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,240
Captain Wang,

265
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,290
those two guys were seen

266
00:13:00,290 --> 00:13:02,220
driving a car away half an hour ago.

267
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,190
Hand out photos of them.

268
00:13:05,390 --> 00:13:06,750
Notify all checkpoints.

269
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:08,320
Don't let them leave Sanjiangkou.

270
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:08,720
Got it.

271
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:11,300
Listen,

272
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,100
Team 1, Team 2,

273
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:12,750
follow me!

274
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:37,340
My little grandson

275
00:13:37,340 --> 00:13:39,390
took one yuan with him
and went to buy a popsicle.

276
00:13:39,390 --> 00:13:40,600
But those two men robbed him

277
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,910
just as he reached that alley entrance.

278
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:43,370
He's just a six-year-old.

279
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:44,120
See,

280
00:13:44,630 --> 00:13:45,670
in this neighborhood,

281
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:46,670
all women—

282
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,520
each and every woman—

283
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,790
would never hang

284
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,480
their washed underware outside.

285
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:51,960
That's right.

286
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:52,960
Or it'd be stolen.

287
00:13:53,270 --> 00:13:55,130
What kind of person would do that?

288
00:13:56,730 --> 00:13:57,610
Thank you all.

289
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,260
The clues you provided

290
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,320
are helpful for our investigation.

291
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:02,520
Just hurry and arrest

292
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,360
those two scumbags.

293
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,000
Yes, arrest them.

294
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,960
We will. Rest assured.

295
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:05,430
Thank you.

296
00:14:05,430 --> 00:14:06,030
Thank you.

297
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:06,880
Thank you too.

298
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:07,850
Thanks a lot.

299
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:09,630
They'll be caught sooner or later.

300
00:14:09,630 --> 00:14:10,750
They're never up to any good, are they?

301
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:11,200
Exactly.

302
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,530
Such peace destroyers.

303
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:22,020
Are they really the culprits?

304
00:14:42,330 --> 00:14:43,820
[Name: Hu Qinghua]

305
00:14:42,550 --> 00:14:44,150
Money solves every problem.

306
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,820
One million US dollars...

307
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:50,010
It's equal to over 60 million yuan.

308
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:52,610
We can each take more than 30 million.

309
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:56,720
With your math skills,

310
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:58,850
it's a shame you're not an accountant.

311
00:14:59,510 --> 00:15:00,480
One million US dollars

312
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:02,210
is equal to over 7 million yuan.

313
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,480
Only 7 million yuan?

314
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:08,750
"Only"?

315
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,750
How much is that God of Wealth statue

316
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:11,510
you moved?

317
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,510
In your entire life,

318
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:14,120
have you ever seen 7 million?

319
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:15,630
I...

320
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:17,700
Splitting 7 million

321
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:19,240
between the two of us...

322
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:21,750
We'll each have only a little
more than 3 million.

323
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,750
That's not even enough to get a wife.

324
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,880
It costs that much to get a wife?

325
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,200
Then this woman can't be your true love.

326
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,520
You made a good point.

327
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:32,080
Listen,

328
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:33,840
do you think true love exists

329
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:34,750
in this world?

330
00:15:37,910 --> 00:15:39,240
When I'm about to dress as a woman,

331
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:39,870
don't ask me

332
00:15:39,870 --> 00:15:41,530
any questions about romance.

333
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:42,960
Okay, got it.

334
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:45,150
Hey,

335
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,630
I'd like to go for
a different makeup style this time

336
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:48,690
as a breakthrough.

337
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:51,640
A breakthrough, huh?

338
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:53,110
I'll help.

339
00:15:55,150 --> 00:15:55,810
Take a look

340
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,840
at these two men. Have you seen them?

341
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,000
Well...

342
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,910
No, never.

343
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,240
Did you look carefully?

344
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,300
Take a closer look.

345
00:16:12,910 --> 00:16:14,970
Sir, careful. The floor is slippery.

346
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:29,200
I really haven't seen them.

347
00:16:30,630 --> 00:16:31,790
Show me the registration record

348
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:32,630
of guests then.

349
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:33,510
Well, I...

350
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:34,960
What? Hurry!

351
00:16:38,090 --> 00:16:38,950
Sorry for that.

352
00:16:52,670 --> 00:16:53,880
There isn't even a photo.

353
00:16:53,880 --> 00:16:55,610
How do I understand any of this?

354
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:57,510
Gosh. Look.

355
00:16:57,510 --> 00:16:58,480
Such messy handwriting.

356
00:16:58,480 --> 00:16:59,510
H-How can I read this?

357
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:01,110
Do you know what it says here?

358
00:17:13,589 --> 00:17:15,109
You're disguising as a blind man now.

359
00:17:15,109 --> 00:17:17,000
Acting like this will blow your cover.

360
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:17,730
Give it to me.

361
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,510
Watch me.

362
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:29,910
You have a try.

363
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:35,650
Is it passable?

364
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:42,090
Come on, give me a hand.

365
00:17:42,550 --> 00:17:43,550
I'm blind now.

366
00:17:55,030 --> 00:17:56,640
Those two bastards.

367
00:17:58,510 --> 00:18:00,030
Where have they gone?

368
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:30,400
I just sighed. Did it affect you or what?

369
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:31,310
No.

370
00:18:31,350 --> 00:18:32,520
The car is out of gas.

371
00:18:33,270 --> 00:18:34,270
Then go get some gas.

372
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:35,470
Why did you pull over?

373
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:37,210
It's completely out of gas.

374
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,400
Did you step on

375
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,400
the gas pedal too hard?

376
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:42,750
This car is even older than me.

377
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:43,950
I wish I could do that.

378
00:18:53,110 --> 00:18:53,840
What do we do?

379
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:58,970
We'll have to push the car.

380
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:01,100
I pulled over at the perfect spot.

381
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,200
The sign here says

382
00:19:02,210 --> 00:19:03,350
there is a gas station

383
00:19:03,350 --> 00:19:04,680
800 meters to the right.

384
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,930
Get out and push the car now.

385
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:12,440
I guess it's the only option.

386
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:16,590
Join me.

387
00:19:17,110 --> 00:19:18,310
But I have to stay in the car

388
00:19:18,310 --> 00:19:19,840
to spin the steering wheel.

389
00:19:20,030 --> 00:19:21,400
You can do it and push the car
at the same time.

390
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,320
Just keep that door open.

391
00:19:22,320 --> 00:19:22,640
No.

392
00:19:22,660 --> 00:19:24,200
-You can't drive.
-Then use this arm to...

393
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:24,590
I...

394
00:19:25,070 --> 00:19:26,070
So you don't know.

395
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:28,650
For safety reasons, both hands

396
00:19:29,030 --> 00:19:29,760
must be on it.

397
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:34,440
You really are...

398
00:19:35,080 --> 00:19:36,290
Fine then.

399
00:19:37,010 --> 00:19:42,000
[Gas Station is 800 meters away
on the right]

400
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:40,210
Come on.

401
00:19:42,540 --> 00:19:43,230
Push!

402
00:19:47,810 --> 00:19:48,450
Push.

403
00:19:50,750 --> 00:19:51,510
Quick.

404
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:57,440
F-Forgot to release the handbrake.

405
00:20:06,490 --> 00:20:10,380
[Diesel Oil]

406
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:20,160
Ma'am,

407
00:20:20,350 --> 00:20:21,760
500 yuan, pump No. 3.

408
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:22,980
Please pay inside.

409
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:24,510
Thank you, young man.

410
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:29,300
How much in gas?

411
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:30,350
Two hundred yuan.

412
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,460
Are we out of RMB notes?

413
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,030
See,

414
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:40,240
I'm blind now.

415
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:57,250
I can't stand on my feet now.

416
00:20:57,250 --> 00:20:58,530
What is it with you?

417
00:20:58,750 --> 00:20:59,400
What now?

418
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:01,340
Take out your money, alright?

419
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,920
Wait. You don't have money?

420
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:03,350
No, I don't.

421
00:21:03,350 --> 00:21:04,610
I only have 2 yuan left.

422
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:06,770
Only 2 yuan in my pocket.

423
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:10,790
Hurry.

424
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,150
What's wrong?

425
00:21:18,590 --> 00:21:20,120
They don't take US dollars.

426
00:21:20,490 --> 00:21:22,060
Are they crazy,

427
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:23,690
for rejecting US dollars?

428
00:21:24,590 --> 00:21:25,720
Where are you going?

429
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:29,240
Come back!

430
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:34,890
What are you going to do?

431
00:21:34,890 --> 00:21:36,110
Hey, ma'am, I have a question.

432
00:21:36,110 --> 00:21:38,590
-Why don't you take US dollars?
-Alright, stop it.

433
00:21:38,590 --> 00:21:39,500
My husband is grumpy.

434
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:40,680
-Sorry.
-We don't take US dollars.

435
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:41,910
Why not?

436
00:21:42,350 --> 00:21:43,750
Give me what you earned by selling junk

437
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:44,410
yesterday.

438
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:46,110
This is all I have.

439
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:48,980
What? But I asked for
200-yuan worth of gas.

440
00:21:48,980 --> 00:21:50,330
Why that much?

441
00:21:51,110 --> 00:21:52,310
Gas is expensive now.

442
00:22:00,030 --> 00:22:00,760
The key's in.

443
00:22:07,790 --> 00:22:08,750
-What kind of attitude is this?
-Let's just go.

444
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:09,800
This is China.

445
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,440
We don't take US dollars.

446
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:10,880
What's the point

447
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:11,680
of saying all that?

448
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,350
Where is your manager?

449
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:13,270
I demand to see your manager.

450
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:14,270
The car! Our car!

451
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:15,620
This isn't over.

452
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:17,590
You haven't paid!

453
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:23,690
Get out of my car, you bastards!

454
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:24,890
What do we do?

455
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:30,850
Get in this taxi!

456
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:33,770
♪ The sun is setting ♪

457
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:41,510
Sir, 200 yuan.

458
00:22:42,740 --> 00:22:43,460
Pay up!

459
00:22:43,480 --> 00:22:44,720
You haven't paid up!

460
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:49,790
What a nice car.

461
00:22:49,820 --> 00:22:51,010
So luxurious.

462
00:22:51,550 --> 00:22:52,710
Leather interiors.

463
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,440
Look at this sunroof.

464
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:57,430
How very nice.

465
00:22:58,520 --> 00:23:00,380
-That scared me.
-That scared me.

466
00:23:02,660 --> 00:23:03,460
Darn it!

467
00:23:04,390 --> 00:23:04,910
Darn it!

468
00:23:05,670 --> 00:23:06,760
Eyes on the road!

469
00:23:08,850 --> 00:23:09,360
No.

470
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:10,450
How is it...

471
00:23:11,030 --> 00:23:11,720
back to us?

472
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:13,240
P-Please stop

473
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:14,070
saying that.

474
00:23:14,070 --> 00:23:14,880
Are we...

475
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,140
being haunted or what?

476
00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:21,490
Bro, drive faster.

477
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,640
Faster, please.

478
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:25,730
I can't see those guys anymore.

479
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:27,900
This is the car we abandoned.

480
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,300
This is as fast as it gets.

481
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:31,310
Bro,

482
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:32,750
there is a suitcase.

483
00:23:32,750 --> 00:23:34,280
It looks identical to ours.

484
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:46,750
Bro,

485
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:49,610
the content is completely different.

486
00:23:50,300 --> 00:23:52,030
Tell me something I don't know.

487
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:53,880
What should we do?

488
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:57,080
Find those two bastards first.

489
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:01,000
Zip the suitcase!

490
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,000
You go open it.

491
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:18,700
See what's inside.

492
00:24:21,270 --> 00:24:22,000
No, I refuse.

493
00:24:22,110 --> 00:24:22,770
You go do it.

494
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,460
I already did it last time.

495
00:24:26,550 --> 00:24:27,000
You...

496
00:24:27,030 --> 00:24:27,880
Just go do it!

497
00:24:29,540 --> 00:24:30,300
Go!

498
00:25:11,690 --> 00:25:12,870
Gosh.

499
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:14,160
What? What is it?

500
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:15,940
Another dead body?

501
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:21,410
A real surprise.

502
00:25:21,870 --> 00:25:22,720
Gosh.

503
00:25:22,750 --> 00:25:23,400
Take a look.

504
00:25:23,400 --> 00:25:23,960
No way.

505
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:24,620
You have to!

506
00:25:25,880 --> 00:25:26,390
Look!

507
00:25:35,390 --> 00:25:38,040
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

508
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:39,030
We're rich now, bro!

509
00:25:38,830 --> 00:25:40,220
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

510
00:25:39,110 --> 00:25:40,710
These are US dollars, right?

511
00:25:41,650 --> 00:25:44,100
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

512
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:43,450
We have to go.

513
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:45,070
Why?

514
00:25:44,970 --> 00:25:46,450
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

515
00:25:45,090 --> 00:25:46,000
This car is too conspicuous.

516
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:47,130
We can't drive this.

517
00:25:47,790 --> 00:25:48,990
Then how do we go home?

518
00:25:52,590 --> 00:25:53,110
By bus.

519
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:57,300
Okay.

520
00:25:57,590 --> 00:25:58,120
Let's go.

521
00:26:00,520 --> 00:26:03,040
♪ Get your head in the game,
we're all smart people here ♪

522
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:06,420
♪ Don't drag your feet,
even gold slips through slow hands ♪

523
00:26:07,130 --> 00:26:08,740
♪ I beat it, I beat it ♪

524
00:26:09,540 --> 00:26:11,460
♪ Aye aye aye aye yo ♪

525
00:26:15,420 --> 00:26:17,980
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

526
00:26:16,280 --> 00:26:18,950
[No parking on the pavement;
violators will be fined 500 yuan]

527
00:26:18,930 --> 00:26:20,250
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

528
00:26:19,510 --> 00:26:19,990
Get out of the car.

529
00:26:19,990 --> 00:26:20,790
What's wrong?

530
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:24,150
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

531
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,330
You want to be arrested?

532
00:26:25,100 --> 00:26:26,580
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

533
00:26:27,490 --> 00:26:29,790
[No parking on the pavement;
violators will be fined 500 yuan]

534
00:26:30,820 --> 00:26:35,200
[Pull up here for a check]

535
00:26:38,970 --> 00:26:45,920
[Temporary checkpoint
for major quarantine forest pests]

536
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:46,210
Chief Zhang.

537
00:26:46,450 --> 00:26:47,430
How is it going?

538
00:26:48,030 --> 00:26:49,030
No finding so far.

539
00:26:55,310 --> 00:26:56,970
Let's go to the next spot then.

540
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:57,440
Okay.

541
00:26:57,830 --> 00:26:58,510
Keep a close eye.

542
00:26:58,510 --> 00:26:58,910
Got it.

543
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:01,320
Good work.

544
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,970
Understood, Captain Wang.

545
00:27:06,950 --> 00:27:10,300
[Temporary checkpoint
for major quarantine forest pests]

546
00:27:11,290 --> 00:27:12,610
Xing, pull over.

547
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:15,280
What's up?

548
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:22,210
Xing, go check out that car.

549
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:08,270
Uncle!

550
00:28:09,590 --> 00:28:10,160
Uncle!

551
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:13,240
When will we go fight Zhou Rong?

552
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,440
Now.

553
00:28:17,120 --> 00:28:19,050
Everyone, come down and follow me!

554
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:23,810
What's this for?

555
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:26,730
For fighting Zhou Rong.

556
00:28:28,110 --> 00:28:29,540
To fight Zhou Rong,

557
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:31,750
we'll use this.

558
00:28:32,110 --> 00:28:32,790
This?

559
00:28:35,550 --> 00:28:38,280
Zhou Rong took away
the ninth piece of bianzhong.

560
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:39,510
Don't you think

561
00:28:39,510 --> 00:28:40,880
he craves the remaining pieces?

562
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:41,900
Of course he does.

563
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,130
How will he get them?

564
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:44,160
He definitely craves them.

565
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:45,290
How will he get them?

566
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,280
So he's waiting

567
00:28:53,350 --> 00:28:55,110
for a call from us?

568
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:56,110
Exactly.

569
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,490
What should we do?

570
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,640
Give him a call!

571
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:01,160
It's hard to find a buyer.

572
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:03,110
It's no easy job to find a seller
either, right?

573
00:29:03,110 --> 00:29:04,880
We will tell him explicitly
that the deal is off.

574
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:06,830
Let's see what he is going to do.

575
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:18,620
He has to double the price,

576
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:21,240
or we won't sell anything to him.

577
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:22,070
Agreed.

578
00:30:18,110 --> 00:30:19,610
Mr. Fang, why a new ride?

579
00:30:19,630 --> 00:30:20,250
Well,

580
00:30:20,290 --> 00:30:21,620
just trying to keep fit.

581
00:30:22,170 --> 00:30:28,310
[Protect the environment,
safeguard our home.]

582
00:30:38,700 --> 00:30:47,120
[Chief Huang]

583
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:41,680
Get ready for a study session

584
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:43,480
at the Party School in a few days.

585
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:04,610
Last 3 lifts.

586
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:05,710
One.

587
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:06,470
Mr. Zhou,

588
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:07,070
I...

589
00:31:07,100 --> 00:31:07,810
Shuang,

590
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,600
would you leave the room?

591
00:31:10,270 --> 00:31:10,800
Mr. Zhou,

592
00:31:10,910 --> 00:31:11,960
a call from Fang Yong.

593
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:13,720
P-P-Pick it up.

594
00:31:13,910 --> 00:31:14,960
Hello, Mr. Fang.

595
00:31:15,790 --> 00:31:16,560
It's me.

596
00:31:18,350 --> 00:31:18,880
What?

597
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,350
Please don't.

598
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:24,200
That was just a little accident.

599
00:31:24,200 --> 00:31:24,640
He...

600
00:31:25,590 --> 00:31:27,250
Okay, I'll tell Mr. Zhou then.

601
00:31:29,890 --> 00:31:30,630
This is...

602
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:32,070
No way.

603
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:35,200
Hello.

604
00:31:35,550 --> 00:31:36,080
Speak up.

605
00:31:37,270 --> 00:31:38,070
Help me...

606
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:40,460
Hello?

607
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,440
You failed such a trivial task.

608
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:44,640
What's the point of keeping you around?

609
00:31:45,480 --> 00:31:46,700
Fine. G-Go ahead then.

610
00:31:46,700 --> 00:31:47,710
Take your time.

611
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:48,860
I'm listening.

612
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:51,480
That's it.

613
00:31:57,860 --> 00:31:58,390
Mr. Zhou!

614
00:31:58,570 --> 00:31:59,190
Mr. Zhou.

615
00:32:06,150 --> 00:32:07,660
You almost got me killed.

616
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:10,030
I was asking you
to pick up the barbell, not...

617
00:32:10,030 --> 00:32:10,960
Sorry, Mr. Zhou.

618
00:32:11,110 --> 00:32:13,770
I thought you were asking me
to pick up the phone.

619
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,060
What happened?

620
00:32:16,590 --> 00:32:17,590
Fang Yong called,

621
00:32:19,070 --> 00:32:20,870
cancelling the bianzhong deal.

622
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:21,920
Why?

623
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:23,930
I don't know.

624
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:25,680
Wait.

625
00:32:26,350 --> 00:32:27,480
Zhu Yifei just refused to sell,

626
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:29,640
and he immediately said he wouldn't buy?

627
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:31,040
Could it be a concidence?

628
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:33,550
Besides, Li Penggai called just now,

629
00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:35,750
saying he couldn't find those two guys.

630
00:32:36,110 --> 00:32:37,040
In Sanjiangkou,

631
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:39,110
is there anyone I can't find?

632
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,010
Mr. Zhou,

633
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:41,270
the happenings in recent days

634
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:42,310
are so weird.

635
00:32:42,750 --> 00:32:43,550
Is the person after us

636
00:32:43,550 --> 00:32:44,720
really that powerful?

637
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:45,250
I mean...

638
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:03,400
When those two people are caught
and their phones checked,

639
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:05,330
there's nothing we can say to help.

640
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:06,120
Mr. Zhou,

641
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:08,840
it's time you took medicine.

642
00:33:19,340 --> 00:33:20,900
I once went a week

643
00:33:20,930 --> 00:33:22,370
without taking this medicine,

644
00:33:22,370 --> 00:33:23,900
and I didn't have a relapse.

645
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:25,000
Do you believe it?

646
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,010
I've told you about it.

647
00:33:29,550 --> 00:33:30,920
I spent an entire week

648
00:33:31,470 --> 00:33:33,200
on that small island Gondwana.

649
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,070
I didn't have to think about

650
00:33:34,070 --> 00:33:34,550
anything there.

651
00:33:34,550 --> 00:33:35,810
I did nothing but eat and sleep every day.

652
00:33:35,810 --> 00:33:36,880
I didn't take a single pill,

653
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:38,390
and I didn't have a relapse.

654
00:33:38,390 --> 00:33:39,440
I swore at that time

655
00:33:39,440 --> 00:33:42,300
that one day I'd stop taking this medicine
for good!

656
00:33:42,310 --> 00:33:42,880
Jianren,

657
00:33:43,590 --> 00:33:44,390
it is high time

658
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:45,680
for me to do so!

659
00:33:48,110 --> 00:33:49,170
So you're planning

660
00:33:49,270 --> 00:33:50,310
to go to Gondwana?

661
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:53,880
What if you have relapses again?

662
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:54,910
Nonsense!

663
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:56,790
As I said, relapses won't happen

664
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:58,240
again when I live in Gondwana!

665
00:33:58,240 --> 00:33:58,900
Yes, right.

666
00:33:59,070 --> 00:33:59,680
You'll be fine.

667
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,310
Where am I going?

668
00:34:00,310 --> 00:34:01,000
Gondwana!

669
00:34:01,990 --> 00:34:03,000
I got it, Mr. Zhou.

670
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:04,540
I'll skip town with you.

671
00:34:04,750 --> 00:34:06,480
I've done all the preparation.

672
00:34:07,270 --> 00:34:08,230
What preparation?

673
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:09,230
I learned English

674
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:10,710
for only one purpose:

675
00:34:10,710 --> 00:34:12,080
by the time I'm with you,

676
00:34:12,150 --> 00:34:13,800
there won't be a problem with communition!

677
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:14,810
You're insane.

678
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:17,620
People in Gondwana don't speak English.

679
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,320
Seriously?

680
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:43,400
Bro,

681
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,780
I feel so itchy.

682
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,610
Am I allergic to this?

683
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:48,429
Don't worry. You're not.

684
00:34:48,550 --> 00:34:50,810
It's made from eco-friendly materials.

685
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,840
We only have these two IDs now.

686
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,100
What about the others?

687
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,710
In my suitcase.

688
00:35:06,760 --> 00:35:08,320
This doesn't look like me.

689
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:14,260
And this even looks less like you.

690
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:16,230
What if we're identified

691
00:35:16,230 --> 00:35:17,760
and reported to the police?

692
00:35:19,150 --> 00:35:20,420
We'll have to take a gamble.

693
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:23,470
[Ruihao Boutique Hotel]

694
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,410
A standard room.

695
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:42,630
You IDs?

696
00:36:40,070 --> 00:36:41,270
A deposit of 500 yuan.

697
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:49,740
Forgot to exchange for RMB.
I'll get some tomorrow.

698
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,530
Remember to do that.

699
00:36:53,680 --> 00:36:54,550
Room 209.

700
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:11,880
Sorry about that.

701
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:17,830
Isn't that the blind man
I bumped into before?

702
00:37:43,450 --> 00:37:46,440
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]t

703
00:37:59,020 --> 00:37:59,480
Li Qian.

704
00:38:01,110 --> 00:38:01,910
Captain Wang.

705
00:38:03,670 --> 00:38:05,000
What are you going to do?

706
00:38:05,670 --> 00:38:07,800
I'm going to make a report to the chief.

707
00:38:09,110 --> 00:38:10,030
Weren't you assigned to help

708
00:38:10,030 --> 00:38:10,970
investigate Liu Bei's car?

709
00:38:10,250 --> 00:38:10,460
[Police Visit Record]

710
00:38:10,850 --> 00:38:12,040
[Visit Record]

711
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:12,480
Why would you work on this?

712
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:14,340
I think it's of great importance.

713
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:15,740
I know it's important.

714
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:18,120
So is obeying orders.

715
00:38:20,790 --> 00:38:21,440
Get back to your work.

716
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,320
I will hand this over to Chief Zhang.

717
00:38:21,970 --> 00:38:22,240
[Police Visit Record]

718
00:38:32,380 --> 00:38:34,090
[Scrap yard]

719
00:38:37,600 --> 00:38:38,330
Chief Zhang.

720
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:41,630
This afternoon near Dongxian Road,

721
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:42,360
we found an abandoned car

722
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:43,510
again, a Land Rover.

723
00:38:43,970 --> 00:38:45,250
[Scene Investigation Record]

724
00:38:44,030 --> 00:38:44,920
The car has been examined.

725
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:45,960
It's Lin Kai's car.

726
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:47,030
That taxi from before

727
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:49,030
was the Xiali sedan that ran over Lin Kai.

728
00:38:49,030 --> 00:38:50,370
These two cars were both

729
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,600
tinted and modified.

730
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:53,160
Any clues in the car?

731
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:55,440
Four sets of fingerprints were found.

732
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,550
They're being compared one by one.

733
00:38:56,550 --> 00:38:57,320
Four people?

734
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:03,050
What is this?

735
00:39:03,110 --> 00:39:04,800
The stuff we found
in the trunk of the Land Rover.

736
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,230
A big box of makeup products,

737
00:39:06,230 --> 00:39:07,250
plus many

738
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:08,110
fake IDs.

739
00:39:11,400 --> 00:39:12,340
And this.

740
00:39:14,030 --> 00:39:15,000
Today, Li Qian visited

741
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,160
the scrap yard

742
00:39:15,380 --> 00:39:17,120
[Police Visit Record]

743
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,230
and nearby residents.

744
00:39:17,230 --> 00:39:17,880
According to them,

745
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:19,280
Xiao Mao and Xia Tinggang

746
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,590
are just two street loafers

747
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:22,150
who can hardly count as hooligans.

748
00:39:22,150 --> 00:39:23,230
They couldn't have committed

749
00:39:23,230 --> 00:39:24,760
robbery and murder, right?

750
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,000
Chief.

751
00:39:36,230 --> 00:39:36,710
Chief,

752
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,110
I really don't think

753
00:39:38,110 --> 00:39:40,570
Xiao Mao and Xia Tinggang
are the murderers.

754
00:39:40,590 --> 00:39:42,840
The killing was likely done
by two other people.

755
00:39:42,840 --> 00:39:43,510
Should we expand

756
00:39:43,510 --> 00:39:45,310
the scope of the investigation?

757
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,570
[That young man named Li Penggai often
comes collect scrap materials at my home]

758
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,670
It says here that when Li Penggai

759
00:39:50,570 --> 00:39:51,870
[He seems honest]

760
00:39:52,030 --> 00:39:53,760
first arrived at Sanjiangkou,

761
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,630
he worked for over a year

762
00:39:55,630 --> 00:39:57,090
with Mao and Xia Tinggang.

763
00:39:57,700 --> 00:39:58,880
Is it true?

764
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:01,480
It's known to all the old neighbors.

765
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:05,220
[Xia Tinggang]

766
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:05,500
After spending only a bit over one year

767
00:40:05,500 --> 00:40:07,100
learning from these two men,

768
00:40:07,630 --> 00:40:09,320
he managed to become the most favored

769
00:40:09,320 --> 00:40:11,790
[Hu Jianren] [Lang Bowen] [Mei Dong]

770
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:12,490
security team leader
in Zhou Rong's company.

771
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,320
Are Mao and Xia Tinggang really

772
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:17,520
just street loafers?

773
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:20,710
Right now, we're looking everywhere

774
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:21,840
for them in the city.

775
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:22,590
It's been a whole day,

776
00:40:22,590 --> 00:40:23,920
yet there isn't a trace of them.

777
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:25,650
Could ordinary street loafers

778
00:40:26,030 --> 00:40:26,840
such strong

779
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,840
counter-reconnaissance skills?\

780
00:40:31,590 --> 00:40:33,190
[Xia Tinggang] [Mao Hongwei]
[Suspects of the jewelry store robbery]

781
00:40:34,710 --> 00:40:36,110
Such sadness in the eyes.

782
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,620
I can't read your mind.

783
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:44,420
Before new findings are made,

784
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:47,250
our focus is still on Mao
and Xia Tinggang.

785
00:40:46,270 --> 00:40:47,400
[Xia Tinggang] [Mao Hongwei]
[Suspects of the jewelry store robbery]

786
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:48,360
That said, we truly

787
00:40:48,360 --> 00:40:50,030
need to expand the scope of search.

788
00:40:50,030 --> 00:40:51,250
Don't think of them

789
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,360
as ordinary street loafers.

790
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:54,090
Check all the inns and hotels.

791
00:40:54,190 --> 00:40:55,400
I have a hunch that these two people

792
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:56,630
are experts in disguise.

793
00:40:56,630 --> 00:40:57,280
Besides

794
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:58,720
their photos,

795
00:40:58,880 --> 00:40:59,920
distribute pictures

796
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:00,880
of this suitcase as well.

797
00:41:00,880 --> 00:41:02,190
Carry out a thorough investigation

798
00:41:02,190 --> 00:41:03,400
whenever two men are found carrying

799
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:04,280
such a suitcase.

800
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:04,680
Got it.

801
00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,160
Captain Wang.

802
00:41:13,630 --> 00:41:15,880
You and the Chief can't treat me
like this.

803
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,400
I should be the one saying that.

804
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:17,860
Li Qian,

805
00:41:18,230 --> 00:41:19,490
what's wrong with you?

806
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:21,880
You do the exact opposite
of what the Chief says

807
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:22,760
and you keep picking on him.

808
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:23,880
What are you trying to do?

809
00:41:23,880 --> 00:41:24,880
I do it because you and the Chief

810
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,110
plan to transfer me off the front lines.

811
00:41:26,110 --> 00:41:27,030
Who's planning to do that?

812
00:41:27,030 --> 00:41:28,030
You and the Chief.

813
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:29,110
Did the Chief assign me

814
00:41:29,110 --> 00:41:30,840
to watch surveillance footage

815
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:33,150
because Director Gao wants to keep me
from the danger on the front line?

816
00:41:33,150 --> 00:41:34,280
Don't think I'm unaware of it.

817
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:35,070
Who told you that?

818
00:41:35,070 --> 00:41:35,710
It doesn't matter.

819
00:41:35,710 --> 00:41:36,440
Just tell me if it's true or not.

820
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:37,440
No, it's not true.

821
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:39,480
Chief Zhang only told everyone

822
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,800
to try to keep you safe.

823
00:41:41,280 --> 00:41:42,440
This has nothing to do
with you being assigned

824
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:43,840
to watch surveillance footage.

825
00:41:43,840 --> 00:41:44,300
Really?

826
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:44,780
Really.

827
00:41:46,070 --> 00:41:47,270
See, you're actually

828
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:47,940
brilliant.

829
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:48,710
Why not use

830
00:41:48,710 --> 00:41:50,360
your brain for cases instead?

831
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:51,630
When anything comes up, try looking

832
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:52,630
for the cause in yourself.

833
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:53,710
You think there are 4 suspects.

834
00:41:53,710 --> 00:41:54,400
Is there enough proof?

835
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,640
Who are the other two? Where are they?

836
00:41:55,640 --> 00:41:56,230
Why did they do it?

837
00:41:56,230 --> 00:41:57,630
Can you explain all that?

838
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:00,080
Listen,

839
00:42:00,110 --> 00:42:01,260
based on the current clues,

840
00:42:01,260 --> 00:42:03,320
Chief Zhang's deduction is correct.

841
00:42:03,750 --> 00:42:05,550
Don't make trouble out of nothing.

842
00:42:05,550 --> 00:42:06,800
Just go watch surveillance footage.

843
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:07,190
Yes.
